# Phase 4b: Smart Study Roadmap - COMPLETED

## Summary

Implemented the Smart Study Roadmap feature, which provides AI-generated personalized study curricula that adapt weekly based on exam date, study time, and user progress.

## Backend Implementation

### Models (backend/app/models/roadmap.py) - ALREADY EXISTED
- `StudyRoadmap`: Main roadmap model with exam date, study preferences, status, and AI-generated recommendations
- `RoadmapMilestone`: Weekly milestones with daily study plans and completion criteria
- `MilestoneStatus`: pending, in_progress, completed, skipped
- `RoadmapStatus`: active, paused, completed, archived

### RoadmapGenerator Service (backend/app/services/roadmap_generator.py) - ALREADY EXISTED
- `create_roadmap()`: Generates personalized curriculum based on exam date and study time
- `adapt_roadmap()`: Adjusts remaining milestones based on current performance
- `get_daily_plan()`: Retrieves study plan for a specific date
- `update_milestone_progress()`: Tracks milestone completion
- Scheduling algorithm allocates domains across weeks based on PMP 2026 ECO weights (People 33%, Process 41%, Business Environment 26%)
- Prioritizes weak domains identified from user analytics

### API Endpoints (backend/app/routers/roadmap.py) - ALREADY EXISTED
- `POST /api/roadmap/create` - Create new study roadmap
- `GET /api/roadmap/active` - Get user's active roadmap
- `GET /api/roadmap/{id}` - Get specific roadmap
- `GET /api/roadmap/{id}/daily/{date}` - Get daily study plan
- `PUT /api/roadmap/{id}/milestones/{mid}` - Update milestone progress
- `POST /api/roadmap/{id}/adapt` - Adapt roadmap to progress
- `DELETE /api/roadmap/{id}` - Archive roadmap

